des:
Listen to daily updates from Gary Vee! You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". 

Gary Vee is the CEO of Varner Media which works with fortune 100 clients and is also the Chairman of Vaynerx. Gary has a very unique style of communication his message with a very direct and in your face approach. The consensus around Gary’s persona online is that either you love him or you hate him, but he definitely wins in the attention arbitrage race.
